701
01:09:38.412 --> 01:09:40.714
<i>This is not a business negotiation.</i>

702
01:09:40.814 --> 01:09:44.818
<i>I meant what I said about
the consequences of non-compliance.</i>

703
01:09:44.918 --> 01:09:47.722
