01:13:42.423 --> 01:13:45.276
We need to go. Now.

736
01:13:46.527 --> 01:13:48.979
I'll see you later.

737
01:13:53.534 --> 01:13:56.937
"He's just a frightened kid", yet he's
managed to take out one of our men

738
01:13:57.037 --> 01:13:59.240
