in a potentially difficult position.

752
01:15:48.281 --> 01:15:51.485
You mean, that leaves me
potentially bankrupt

753
01:15:51.585 --> 01:15:54.187
and you potentially unemployed? Hm?

754
01:15:54.287 --> 01:15:58.379
